column5: www.islandreefjob.com  Well my application made it through the first round of judges. And now I need your Vote. Just shoot me your email--so I can forward the link for you to vote--look at my DOWN UNDER VIDEO THIS IS THE BEST JOB IN THE WORLD Now when your vote goes through--AND if I win the contest--all names go into a hat and our MAJOR OF MARKHAM will draw 4 names and you will go with me for your all paid expense for three weeks as I work on the GREAT BARRIER REEF. You can enjoy EXTREME FISHING at its best or laze around and explore. THIS IS NO JOKE. Check out the WEB SITE and help me get the job. The site is very busy --so keep trying  CHEERS  AND THANKS  SIMCOEBOB
E:MAIL  BOB  FOR  DETAILS......AND IT COSTS YOU NOTHING.
Most contests like that are just a ploy to get your email address.
actually check out the web site and learn.....I do believe this job has been all over the globe for weeks now...
